<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy</title>

  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- Font Awesome for Icons -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">

  <link rel="icon" href="/logo.jpeg" type="image/icon type">

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background-image: url('/image.jpg'); /* Background image path */
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: center center;
      background-attachment: fixed;
      background-size: cover;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .container {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      max-width: 900px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 120px auto 40px;
      height: 75vh;
      overflow-y: auto;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    h1, h2 {
      opacity: 0;
      animation: slideIn 1.2s ease forwards;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }

    @keyframes slideIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 38px;
      color: #e1b12c;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation-delay: 0.3s;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin: 20px 0 10px;
      color: #f5d179;
      animation-delay: 0.6s;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .icon-text {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .icon-text i {
      margin-right: 10px;
      color: #f5d179;
    }

    /* Buttons */
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: #d6b560;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      transform: scale(0.95);
      animation: bounceIn 1s ease forwards;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #e1b337;
      transform: scale(1);
    }

    .btn:focus {
      outline: none;
    }

    .icon {
      color: #f5d179;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }

    @keyframes bounceIn {
      0% {
        transform: scale(0.8);
        opacity: 0.5;
      }
      100% {
        transform: scale(1);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    #back-btn {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container {
        padding: 20px;
        height: auto;
        margin-top: 60px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1><i class="fas fa-user-shield icon"></i>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>At GitHelper, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when registering or using our services, such as:</p>
    
    <div class="icon-text"><i class="fas fa-user icon"></i> Name</div>
    <div class="icon-text"><i class="fas fa-envelope icon"></i> Email Address</div>
    <div class="icon-text"><i class="fas fa-phone icon"></i> Phone Number</div>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We may use the information we collect from you in the following ways:</p>
    
    <div class="icon-text"><i class="fas fa-handshake icon"></i> To personalize your experience on our website.</div>
    <div class="icon-text"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt icon"></i> To improve customer service and respond to your inquiries.</div>
    <div class="icon-text"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane icon"></i> To send periodic emails regarding your account or our services.</div>

    <h2>Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal identification information to others.</p>
    
    <div id="back-btn">
      <a href="/" class="btn"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left icon"></i>Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
